## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources consulted. While the selected sources provide a broad overview, they may not capture all regional variations or the latest policy developments. Additionally, the complexity of homelessness as a social issue means that some contributing factors may not be fully explored within the constraints of this report. Further research and data collection are necessary to develop a more comprehensive understanding of the problem and potential solutions.